            tryptophan and other essential amino acids that the body cannot
            produce.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="roundtxt-column2">
          <img
            class="collagen-round-image"
            src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0669/6343/9927/files/Mask_group_71_24a3e316-77e8-4643-b299-c37496438024.png?v=1675943080"
          />
          <p>
            Amino acids need Vitamin C, Zinc and Copper to be absorbed. Neither
