        />
        <p>
          Red Algae offers the same benefits for skin, joints, bones and guts as
          collagen—but when combined together it can yield even better results.
          Our drink which contains red algae and collagen—two of nature's most
          beneficial ingredients for skin, joints, bones and guts—is twice as
          effective at improving these areas than the leading competitor (that
          doesn't contain red algae).
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

